'''Derek Thompson''' is an artist who worked on [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']] and wrote and drew the ''[[Sithisis]]'' comic for ''[[Star Wars: Visionaries]]''. He also contributed art to [[Daniel Wallace]]'s [[The Jedi Path: A Manual for Students of the Force (real-life book)|''The Jedi Path: A Manual for Students of the Force'']].

